    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional specimen that redefines the standard for pre-owned excellence. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, shielded from the elements since day one. The exterior finish retains its deep, glass-like luster, recently treated with a multi-stage paint correction and professional-grade ceramic coating\u2014there are absolutely no swirl marks, rock chips, or imperfections to be found. Step inside to an interior that still carries the distinct aroma of fresh factory leather. The seat bolsters remain firm and free of any entry-exit creasing, while the high-resolution displays and switchgear show zero signs of use. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach; it includes a comprehensive binder of every service interval performed exclusively by certified master technicians using only genuine OEM parts. The alloy wheels are pristine with no curb rash, wrapped in premium performance tires with nearly full tread depth. This is a time-capsule quality vehicle for the discerning enthusiast who demands perfection without compromise.",
